{
  "texts": [
    "Following HQ-SAM [33], we use the model trained on HQSeg-44K for direct evaluation on COCO in the zero-shot manner.",
    "As summarized in Tab.",
    "4, our method demonstrates superior performance across various metrics.",
    "Specifically, ELE-SAM achieves 50.6% Average Precision (AP), outperforming SAM (48.5%), HQ-SAM (49.5%), and PA-SAM [34] (49.9%).",
    "The results validate that our ELE-SAM also maintain the generalization capability."
  ]
}